				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Xu%C3%A2n-L%C3%B4i/Di%E1%BB%87p-m%C3%A3-nhi-ph%C3%BA/poem-9s5DpVQjHsixE2k1b-RLdA">Diệp mã nhi phú - 葉馬兒賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Xu%C3%A2n-L%C3%B4i/author-6rhfZvRmtlyU1Z-Y69osfw">Đoàn Xuân Lôi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Di%E1%BB%85m/H%E1%BB%93-gi%C3%A0-th%E1%BA%ADp-b%C3%A1t-ph%C3%A1ch-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-11-ph%C3%A1ch/poem-C-VzzyzUjvktXMscD7ahJg">Hồ già thập bát phách - đệ 11 phách - 胡笳十八拍－第十一拍</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Di%E1%BB%85m/author-EhbmJp2hi9HLiXQfO6maGA">Thái Diễm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/L%E1%BA%A1c-th%E1%BA%A7n-ph%C3%BA/poem-ylYQnboi4bp_70hzYu0a0Q">Lạc thần phú - 洛神賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author-3mdeOfneLQCMOxlLrV12_w">Tào Thực</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/L%E1%BB%99c-%C4%90%E1%BA%A7u-s%C6%A1n/poem-2XLploFvmhZZqqDis2WymA">Lộc Đầu sơn - 鹿頭山</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/Ly-B%E1%BA%AFc-Kinh/poem-rrvmSkDzDCN9_y8ophV3cw">Ly Bắc Kinh - 離北京</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Ch%C3%AD-Minh/author-a7YEflJr1_rcFKC9dgECgQ">Hồ Chí Minh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Ly-tao/poem-lRoe60dlSbBq5oc1ZRJWhQ">Ly tao - 離騷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/M%C3%A3-Ng%C3%B4i-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-wPAb7iGm60f9gS3isob18Q">Mã Ngôi  kỳ 1 - 馬嵬其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-Th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%E1%BA%A8n/author-9iJ5oLtFQBkuT0Ej5xvn9Q">Lý Thư